1
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:13,100
<i>I still want our family
to reunite</i>

2
00:00:13,233 --> 00:00:16,133
<i>because I want Mommy Emma,
not you!</i>

3
00:00:16,267 --> 00:00:17,567
<i> Enough!</i>

4
00:00:17,700 --> 00:00:20,800
<i>Olive, that's enough.
Let's put an end to this.</i>

5
00:00:20,933 --> 00:00:23,900
<i>I can't stand
your wickedness anymore.</i>

6
00:00:27,533 --> 00:00:29,200
<i> Aunt Astrid!</i>

7
00:00:32,733 --> 00:00:34,167
<i> Mookie!</i>

8
00:00:34,333 --> 00:00:35,733
<i> You've made it.</i>

9
00:00:35,867 --> 00:00:37,600
<i> You've made it to hell.</i>

10
00:01:18,333 --> 00:01:19,867
Mommy.

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,433
Mommy, please.

12
00:01:21,567 --> 00:01:22,667
I'm begging you.

13
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:25,033
Please don't hurt my mom.

14
00:01:25,167 --> 00:01:28,300
I've run out of mercy
for all of you!

15
00:01:29,833 --> 00:01:33,333
You should all die!

16
00:01:33,467 --> 00:01:35,100
You're the one who fooled us.

17
00:01:35,233 --> 00:01:37,467
You played with our feelings,
Olive!

18
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,500
Olive, you should stop.

19
00:01:39,633 --> 00:01:41,700
Are you tired of playing?

20
00:01:43,367 --> 00:01:44,500
Are you tired, Emma?

21
00:01:45,667 --> 00:01:47,800
- Mommy, please!
- Then let me kill you first!

22
00:01:47,933 --> 00:01:49,767
- Don't!
- Don't!

23
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:51,433
Let go!

24
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:56,333
Stop it!

25
00:01:56,467 --> 00:01:57,667
Olive!

26
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,567
Mom.

27
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,100
I said stop it!

28
00:02:04,233 --> 00:02:06,800
Mom!

29
00:02:06,933 --> 00:02:09,433
Mom!

30
00:02:18,033 --> 00:02:20,600
- Mom!
- Mookie! Mookie!

31
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:35,733
Don't fight anymore.

32
00:02:35,867 --> 00:02:37,667
Our boss will have you killed
later anyway.

33
00:02:44,967 --> 00:02:45,967
Go ahead.

34
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,467
Go on!

35
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:08,700
Emma?

36
00:03:08,833 --> 00:03:10,067
Mookie?

37
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,333
Emma!

38
00:03:15,533 --> 00:03:16,500
Emma?

39
00:03:18,233 --> 00:03:19,700
Mookie?

40
00:03:19,833 --> 00:03:20,967
Are you here?

41
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,000
Emma?

42
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,167
Mookie!

43
00:03:45,433 --> 00:03:47,067
Where's the doctor?

44
00:03:48,033 --> 00:03:49,100
Will this take much longer?

45
00:03:49,233 --> 00:03:50,967
What time can I get out of here?

46
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:53,933
Ligaya, don't be stubborn.

47
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:56,500
You still can't go out.

48
00:03:56,633 --> 00:03:58,900
You need to get some rest.

49
00:03:59,033 --> 00:04:02,967
I'm tired of resting.
I want to see Emma and Mookie.

50
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,500
Hey, calm down!

51
00:04:04,633 --> 00:04:08,400
Zayn and Flor are now
with the rescue team.

52
00:04:08,533 --> 00:04:10,833
They're on their way
to Mookie and Emma.

53
00:04:10,967 --> 00:04:12,933
You can get some rest now.

54
00:04:13,067 --> 00:04:17,433
Unless you want to die first
because of your stubbornness.

55
00:04:17,567 --> 00:04:18,533
Go ahead!

56
00:04:19,733 --> 00:04:22,200
Try to put yourselves
in my shoes!

57
00:04:22,333 --> 00:04:25,500
What if you're the one worrying
about your child and grandchild?

58
00:04:25,633 --> 00:04:28,200
And you're also thinking
about your evil child.

59
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:39,367
Hurry up. Olive might catch us.

60
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:43,367
Wait, my foot hurts.
I think I'm having a cramp.

61
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:44,600
Hold on to me.

62
00:04:44,733 --> 00:04:45,933
Okay.

63
00:04:46,067 --> 00:04:46,800
Hurry up!

64
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:06,167
Boss!

65
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,467
Where's the guy?

66
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,100
He was able to escape.

67
00:05:12,933 --> 00:05:13,933
Let's go!

68
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:20,200
Thank you so much, Mom.

69
00:05:20,333 --> 00:05:22,167
You're always there for me.

70
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:29,133
Your dad and I will protect you
as long as we're alive.

71
00:05:31,267 --> 00:05:33,033
Where's dad?

72
00:05:34,467 --> 00:05:36,000
We were together earlier.

73
00:05:36,133 --> 00:05:37,233
But, wait...

74
00:05:43,267 --> 00:05:44,667
Let's go. Come on.

75
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,500
Ouch, that hurts.

76
00:05:49,633 --> 00:05:50,700
Hurry up.

77
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,100
Hurry.

78
00:05:58,267 --> 00:05:59,733
Dear, hurry up.

79
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:07,133
Hurry up.

80
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:18,533
Mookie! Dear, come here!

81
00:06:18,667 --> 00:06:20,433
Hurry! Let's go there!

82
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,767
My dear...

83
00:06:35,833 --> 00:06:37,433
this, too, shall pass.

84
00:06:38,567 --> 00:06:40,267
After every storm,

85
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,500
a light will shine through.

86
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:46,967
We're close to finding
our happiness, Dear.

87
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:50,867
Soon, we'll be together
again as a family.

88
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,900
Mom...

89
00:06:56,533 --> 00:06:58,833
Mom, thank you so much.

90
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:06,467
Thank you so much
for always being there for me.

91
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:10,433
Even during those moments
when I was so angry at you.

92
00:07:10,567 --> 00:07:12,700
I'm sorry
for getting mad at you.

93
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:15,567
I'm sorry for believing
Mommy Olive

94
00:07:15,733 --> 00:07:17,400
that you don't love me
anymore...

95
00:07:17,533 --> 00:07:22,200
that you abandoned dad and I,
that you left us.

96
00:07:22,333 --> 00:07:23,933
I'm sorry, Mom.

97
00:07:24,067 --> 00:07:26,467
If only I had been smarter,

98
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,467
this wouldn't have happened
to us.

99
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,867
We wouldn't be in trouble
right now.

100
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:34,033
I'm sorry, Mom.
I'm really sorry.

101
00:07:36,333 --> 00:07:38,333
Don't blame yourself.

102
00:07:38,467 --> 00:07:40,433
You did nothing.

103
00:07:40,567 --> 00:07:43,167
It is Olive's fault.

104
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:45,733
She's the one to blame.

105
00:07:45,867 --> 00:07:47,300
My dear...

106
00:07:47,433 --> 00:07:50,333
my love for you
never disappeared.

107
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,000
I knew it.

108
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:45,167
You're still here.

109
00:08:46,767 --> 00:08:47,733
So...

110
00:08:49,267 --> 00:08:50,833
where were we?

111
00:08:50,967 --> 00:08:54,067
Mommy, please, let's stop this.

112
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:57,800
Let me go with Mommy Emma,
please.

113
00:08:57,967 --> 00:09:01,500
Mommy Emma, Mommy Emma,
Mommy Emma!

114
00:09:01,633 --> 00:09:03,467
I'm so sick and tired of you
constantly calling

115
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,067
your Mommy Emma!

116
00:09:06,833 --> 00:09:09,233
Mookie, I only want one thing.

117
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:13,133
I want you to forget that woman!

118
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:17,300
Why do you keep thinking of her?

119
00:09:19,633 --> 00:09:22,333
What do you think I would feel?

120
00:09:22,467 --> 00:09:24,733
Your own mother?

121
00:09:24,867 --> 00:09:28,467
If you don't want to forget
your Mommy Emma...

122
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,767
What about if...

123
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:37,000
I'll make her forget about you.

124
00:09:38,233 --> 00:09:40,500
I don't want to.

125
00:09:40,633 --> 00:09:41,633
Yes...

126
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:46,900
- That's a better idea.
- No. I don't want to.

127
00:09:47,033 --> 00:09:48,700
I'd rather choose death

128
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:53,700
than go on living unloved
and forgotten by you.

129
00:09:53,833 --> 00:09:55,433
Mom, I don't want that.

130
00:09:55,567 --> 00:09:57,033
No, Dear.

131
00:09:57,167 --> 00:09:58,600
No one will forget.

132
00:09:58,733 --> 00:10:00,100
No one will undergo surgery.

133
00:10:00,233 --> 00:10:01,733
No one will get hurt.

134
00:10:04,467 --> 00:10:07,267
I love the confidence, Emma.

135
00:10:10,067 --> 00:10:11,600
I'm so excited.

136
00:10:11,733 --> 00:10:13,033
So...

137
00:10:13,167 --> 00:10:15,067
are you ready?

138
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,400
Ma'am...

139
00:10:16,533 --> 00:10:18,967
the guy she's always with
is here.

140
00:10:19,667 --> 00:10:21,133
Get them.

141
00:10:24,667 --> 00:10:26,267
- Mom!
- Let go of me!

142
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,567
Mommy Olive, please!

143
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:30,067
Dear!

144
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,667
Mookie!

145
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,300
Mommy!

146
00:10:35,267 --> 00:10:37,567
Please, Mommy,
let's talk about this!

147
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,333
- Mommy!
- Mookie!

148
00:10:41,833 --> 00:10:42,900
Go on!

149
00:10:43,033 --> 00:10:43,900
Bring her outside.

150
00:10:49,067 --> 00:10:50,633
Olive, stop this!

151
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:53,733
Mom!

152
00:10:53,867 --> 00:10:55,167
Mommy!

153
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:57,800
Mommy, please. Whatever you're
planning to do to my mom,

154
00:10:57,933 --> 00:10:59,933
please don't do it!

155
00:11:00,067 --> 00:11:02,867
Mommy, I know you have
so much love to give.

156
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:06,200
And you can give it
to others without effort.

157
00:11:06,333 --> 00:11:10,233
Mommy, please. Let's stop this.

158
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,600
Do you know what
you're talking about?

159
00:11:13,633 --> 00:11:16,100
I tried doing all of that.

160
00:11:16,233 --> 00:11:19,067
I tried to be a loving mother,

161
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,500
a loving partner...

162
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:23,000
and I failed.

163
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:27,133
So this is the only option
I have left.

164
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,000
Mommy!

165
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:36,567
Mommy! Mommy, please!

166
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,533
Mom and I will help you.

167
00:11:38,667 --> 00:11:40,167
I'll help you.

168
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,633
I don't need your help.

169
00:11:43,767 --> 00:11:47,700
What I need is your cooperation.

170
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:50,500
- Mommy, please!
- Olive, stop.

171
00:11:50,633 --> 00:11:54,500
Mommy, have mercy on my mom.
She's your sister!

172
00:11:54,633 --> 00:11:56,533
Leave me alone, you animal!

173
00:11:56,667 --> 00:12:00,867
You're the one
who will behave like an animal

174
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:05,433
the moment you forget Mookie.

175
00:12:06,567 --> 00:12:07,933
Mommy!

176
00:12:08,967 --> 00:12:11,033
- Stop!
- Mommy, please, stop!

177
00:12:11,167 --> 00:12:13,367
Mommy!

178
00:12:14,567 --> 00:12:16,800
Mommy, please!

179
00:12:16,933 --> 00:12:20,900
I only want the people
I love to love me back!

180
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,367
But what did they do?

181
00:12:29,133 --> 00:12:32,633
They left me!

182
00:12:32,767 --> 00:12:34,933
Yes, they left you.

183
00:12:35,067 --> 00:12:36,800
That's why you got lonely.

184
00:12:36,933 --> 00:12:39,300
That's why you took Mookie
away from us.

185
00:12:39,433 --> 00:12:42,500
But we believe that you
can start a new life.

186
00:12:42,633 --> 00:12:44,000
We'll help you.

187
00:12:44,133 --> 00:12:45,367
Please stop this.

188
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:48,167
Let us go. I'm begging you.

189
00:12:49,167 --> 00:12:51,267
Why are you blaming me?

190
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:53,667
Mommy, please!

191
00:12:54,267 --> 00:12:58,700
Why does it seem
that everything is my fault?

192
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:06,500
I'm only doing this
because others have wronged me.

193
00:13:08,133 --> 00:13:10,200
Is it my fault...

194
00:13:10,333 --> 00:13:12,600
that your mother gave me away?

195
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,867
Please stop.

196
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,100
Is it my fault

197
00:13:16,233 --> 00:13:19,767
that the people who adopted me
didn't love me?

198
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:21,633
Is it my fault...

199
00:13:23,233 --> 00:13:25,433
that my daughter died?

200
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:33,733
Is it my fault
that I'm being like this?

201
00:13:33,867 --> 00:13:37,867
- Let's end this, Emma!
- Mommy, please!

202
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,233
Mommy, please!

203
00:13:40,367 --> 00:13:42,500
Stop it, Mommy!

204
00:13:42,633 --> 00:13:46,300
My mom might not survive!

205
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,867
Emma?

206
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,033
Mookie?

207
00:13:55,267 --> 00:13:56,367
Emma?

208
00:13:59,233 --> 00:14:00,800
Emma?

209
00:14:00,933 --> 00:14:03,100
Mookie?

210
00:14:03,233 --> 00:14:09,167
Mommy, stop!
My mom might die, please!

211
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:13,600
If she dies in this operation,

212
00:14:13,733 --> 00:14:15,400
then I'm sorry.

213
00:14:15,533 --> 00:14:20,533
Mommy, don't.
Don't do this, please.

214
00:14:20,667 --> 00:14:22,200
We've tried to understand you

215
00:14:22,333 --> 00:14:26,833
after all the evil things
you did to our family!

216
00:14:26,967 --> 00:14:30,100
But no matter how much we
begged, you wouldn't listen.

217
00:14:30,267 --> 00:14:33,400
I won't let you hurt
my family again!

218
00:14:33,533 --> 00:14:34,800
Hey!

219
00:14:34,933 --> 00:14:37,100
Let go of me!

220
00:14:37,233 --> 00:14:38,000
Mommy!

221
00:14:38,467 --> 00:14:39,100
Mom!

222
00:14:39,233 --> 00:14:40,200
Mom.

223
00:14:40,333 --> 00:14:41,433
Mom.

224
00:14:43,033 --> 00:14:43,700
Mom!

225
00:14:49,933 --> 00:14:51,567
Emma!

226
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:52,767
Emma!

227
00:15:10,033 --> 00:15:11,133
Mookie!

228
00:15:24,133 --> 00:15:26,300
- No, Mom!
- Mookie!

229
00:15:43,633 --> 00:15:45,233
Dan! Get Mookie!

230
00:15:45,367 --> 00:15:46,800
Mookie!

231
00:15:46,933 --> 00:15:47,733
Let's go.

232
00:15:47,867 --> 00:15:49,067
Hurry!

233
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,733
Mookie!

234
00:15:52,867 --> 00:15:54,600
Mom!

235
00:15:54,733 --> 00:15:55,300
Mom!

236
00:15:55,433 --> 00:15:58,333
Mommy! Mommy!

237
00:15:58,467 --> 00:16:00,900
- Mommy! Please!
- Stay still! I'm thinking!

238
00:16:01,033 --> 00:16:02,033
Olive!

239
00:16:02,167 --> 00:16:05,067
- Mommy, turn yourself in!
- No!

240
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:08,133
I won't surrender
no matter what happens!

241
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,167
Mommy, you have nowhere else
to go.

242
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:11,333
Surrender yourself,

243
00:16:11,467 --> 00:16:13,633
- so no one gets hurt anymore.
- I know what to do!

244
00:16:13,767 --> 00:16:14,700
We can go this way, Mookie.

245
00:16:14,833 --> 00:16:16,700
- No, Mommy!
- We can escape from here!

246
00:16:16,833 --> 00:16:19,400
- No! Mommy!
- Let's jump and be free.

247
00:16:19,533 --> 00:16:20,467
- Mommy!
- Just the two of us.

248
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,600
- Mommy, no.
- Come on.

249
00:16:21,733 --> 00:16:22,933
Let's be together forever.

250
00:16:23,067 --> 00:16:25,700
- Let's just jump! Come on!
- I don't want to, Mommy!

251
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:28,767
If you don't want to return me
to my family,

252
00:16:28,900 --> 00:16:30,133
at least let me live.

253
00:16:30,267 --> 00:16:33,233
I still have lots of dreams
I want to achieve.

254
00:16:33,367 --> 00:16:34,767
- No, Mookie!
- Mommy.

255
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:35,833
Mommy, please.

256
00:16:35,967 --> 00:16:37,400
- You're only mine.
- No.

257
00:16:37,533 --> 00:16:39,267
You're mine forever, Mookie.

258
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,367
- No.
- You're mine.

259
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:43,133
Come on. Let's start
a new life together.

260
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:44,767
- Come on, let's jump!
- No, no!

261
00:16:51,667 --> 00:16:53,167
Mommy, stop.

262
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:54,300
- Dad! Dad!
- Go ahead!

263
00:16:54,433 --> 00:16:55,733
- I dare you!
- Mom! Mom!

264
00:16:55,867 --> 00:16:57,133
- Go ahead, try it.
- Olive!

265
00:16:57,267 --> 00:16:58,233
Go and take a step,

266
00:16:58,367 --> 00:17:00,833
and I will blow
this kid's head off!

267
00:17:00,967 --> 00:17:05,000
Dan, put your gun down.
Mookie might get shot.

268
00:17:05,133 --> 00:17:06,267
Olive...

269
00:17:07,367 --> 00:17:12,800
when I was newly hired
as your laundry woman,

270
00:17:12,933 --> 00:17:17,067
I saw how protective you were
of Mookie.

271
00:17:18,967 --> 00:17:22,633
Oftentimes, you went overboard.

272
00:17:22,767 --> 00:17:27,200
But I also saw how much it hurt
you whenever Mookie got hurt.

273
00:17:27,333 --> 00:17:29,333
- Shut up!
