295
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,633
Mookie!

296
00:18:19,767 --> 00:18:20,933
Mookie!

297
00:18:21,067 --> 00:18:22,067
Hold on to me!

298
00:18:22,233 --> 00:18:23,267
Mookie!

299
00:18:25,133 --> 00:18:26,400
Mookie!

300
00:18:26,533 --> 00:18:28,033
Olive! Mookie!

301
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,400
- Mookie.
- Mookie!

302
00:18:33,433 --> 00:18:35,333
Where's mommy? Where's mommy?

303
00:18:36,367 --> 00:18:37,767
Mommy?

304
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:40,567
Mommy.

305
00:18:59,067 --> 00:19:00,233
Mommy!

306
00:19:00,367 --> 00:19:02,100
Mommy!

307
00:19:02,233 --> 00:19:03,333
Mommy!

308
00:19:04,267 --> 00:19:06,267
Mommy!

309
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,667
Mommy!

310
00:19:13,533 --> 00:19:15,533
Mommy!

311
00:19:15,667 --> 00:19:18,600
Mommy!

312
00:19:18,733 --> 00:19:22,033
Mommy!

313
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,367
Mommy.

314
00:19:30,433 --> 00:19:33,833
Mommy, I will forever thank you.

315
00:19:37,567 --> 00:19:41,167
You're the first person
I have loved.

316
00:19:42,967 --> 00:19:45,733
I love you so much, Mommy.

317
00:19:45,867 --> 00:19:47,533
I love you so much.

318
00:19:50,133 --> 00:19:51,567
Mommy.

319
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:06,067
Mommy!

320
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:23,800
Dear.

321
00:20:25,067 --> 00:20:28,800
Don't you feel any anger
towards Olive

322
00:20:28,933 --> 00:20:31,333
