to you and our family?

323
00:20:32,933 --> 00:20:34,667
I do.

324
00:20:37,733 --> 00:20:39,000
But you know...

325
00:20:41,667 --> 00:20:43,933
I feel more...

326
00:20:44,933 --> 00:20:46,400
sympathy for mommy.

327
00:20:47,533 --> 00:20:50,533
Her life is so tragic.

328
00:20:50,667 --> 00:20:56,100
All her life, all she has wanted
is someone who will love her.

329
00:20:56,233 --> 00:20:58,600
Someone who will understand her.

330
00:20:59,733 --> 00:21:01,600
Someone who will never
leave her.

331
00:21:03,433 --> 00:21:04,433
But...

332
00:21:06,367 --> 00:21:08,033
