361
00:23:30,633 --> 00:23:34,367
I love you so much, my daughter.
I love you so much.

362
00:23:41,767 --> 00:23:46,067
What's going on?
Why do you keep smiling?

363
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,433
You have a beautiful smile.

364
00:23:47,567 --> 00:23:48,933
You're beautiful.

365
00:23:49,067 --> 00:23:50,467
Oh, come on.

366
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,467
No.

367
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:54,267
Aside from that,

368
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:56,300
I'm happy that your problem
is finally over.

369
00:23:56,467 --> 00:23:57,733
Your family's problem.

370
00:23:59,667 --> 00:24:00,900
I know.

371
00:24:01,567 --> 00:24:04,100
Zayn, thank you so much.

372
00:24:04,933 --> 00:24:09,800
Because you were there when
I needed someone on my side.

373
00:24:09,933 --> 00:24:16,933
So I can focus now on myself,
my family, and school.

374
00:24:19,567 --> 00:24:20,700
And us?

375
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,533
Us.

376
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:40,333
I've been wanting to do this
for a long time.

377
00:24:41,667 --> 00:24:43,200
As they say...

378
00:24:44,867 --> 00:24:46,700
after such a long procession...

379
00:24:47,767 --> 00:24:49,900
after everything
we've been through, Emma...

380
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:52,600
I hope...

381
00:24:54,933 --> 00:24:55,900
I hope...

382
00:24:59,933 --> 00:25:01,033
I hope...

383
00:25:01,167 --> 00:25:03,467
you'll marry me, Emma.

384
00:25:13,867 --> 00:25:15,100
Of course, Dan.

385
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,967
Oh, sorry!

386
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:23,367
- Finally!
- Finally!

387
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:26,533
Finally!

388
00:25:26,667 --> 00:25:28,067
Wow!

389
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:38,100
Long live the newlyweds!

390
00:25:58,033 --> 00:26:01,167
<i>There are different kinds
of mothers.</i>

391
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:04,900
<i>Some are strict
and love intensely.</i>

392
00:26:06,333 --> 00:26:09,767
<i> At first, we think it's okay,</i>

393
00:26:09,933 --> 00:26:11,233
<i> that it's the right way.</i>

394
00:26:11,367 --> 00:26:14,600
<i>Until we realize
that too much of anything</i>

395
00:26:14,733 --> 00:26:18,100
<i> can hurt and suffocate us.</i>

396
00:26:18,233 --> 00:26:20,733
<i> Some mothers are forgiving.</i>

397
00:26:20,867 --> 00:26:22,000
<i> The kind who are willing</i>

398
00:26:22,133 --> 00:26:25,333
<i>to help correct
their children's mistakes.</i>

399
00:26:25,467 --> 00:26:26,867
<i> That's who my Mommy Emma is.</i>

400
00:26:27,900 --> 00:26:29,533
<i> And I'm lucky</i>

401
00:26:29,667 --> 00:26:31,600
<i> because she's my mother.</i>

402
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:36,000
<i> My dearest mother.</i>

403
