Sorry.

414
00:27:23,300 --> 00:27:24,200
Let me take you home.

415
00:27:27,233 --> 00:27:28,567
I can't open it.

416
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:30,033
- It's the other way around.
- The other way around.

417
00:27:30,167 --> 00:27:31,567
I think it's you who's drunk.

418
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:33,333
My feet hurt so much.

419
00:27:35,733 --> 00:27:37,700
