420
00:27:38,733 --> 00:27:40,100
There! There, Mister! Hurry!

421
00:27:40,233 --> 00:27:42,000
Everyone, say something!

422
00:27:42,133 --> 00:27:43,833
There! There, Mister!
Hurry! Hurry!
